OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cool day with a mix of sunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers which will be heavy
OL,7,Fat times with a risk of hail and
OL,8,Fthunder. Mainly light northwesterly
OL,9,Fbreeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome late sunny spells, then
OL,12,Fclear spells overnight, with showers,
OL,13,Fthe showers becoming less frequent and
OL,14,Flighter. Touch of frost possible in
OL,15,Fsheltered spots.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FAnother rather cold day with
OL,18,Fa mix of sunny spells and showers, the
OL,19,Fshowers heavy at times. Winds turning
OL,20,Fnortherly and becoming strong at times
OL,21,Fnear the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
